sourceDescription: This database will detail those persons enumerated in the 1841 Census of England and is an every-name index. In addition, the names of those listed on the population schedule are linked to the actual images of the 1841 Census, reproduced by courtesy of The National Archives, London, England. There are 15,000 records accessible through this database. Learn more...
